chunks.html_content: Apply for a sponsor licence so you can sponsor foreign workers or students to come and work or study in the UK.
chunks.plain_content:
Apply for a sponsor licence
Apply for a sponsor licence so you can sponsor foreign workers or students to come and work or study in the UK.

chunks.html_content: You’ll also need a sponsor licence to employ EEA and Swiss citizens coming to the UK to work from 1 January 2021.
chunks.plain_content:
Apply for a sponsor licence
You’ll also need a sponsor licence to employ EEA and Swiss citizens coming to the UK to work from 1 January 2021.

chunks.html_content:
Read the guide to applying as either:

  • an employer
  • an education provider

You’ll need a credit or debit card to apply for a sponsor licence.
